values-zh-rCN: On sale of every Product; you will receive Primary Points and Secondary Points on the App. You can use the Primary Points to redeem rewards within the app; whereas, Secondary Points are those that get accumulated in your account to reward your customers when they make a sale. These accumulated Secondary Points will be added back to your Primary Points Wallet after 12 months from the date they were awarded in case your customers have not made a sale.
values-ms: Pada jualan setiap produk; anda akan menerima Mata Rendah dan Menengah Mata di App. Anda boleh menggunakan Mata Utama untuk menebus ganjaran dalam aplikasi; sedangkan, Mata menengah adalah mereka yang dapat terkumpul dalam akaun anda untuk memberi ganjaran kepada pelanggan anda apabila mereka membuat jualan. Ini Mata Menengah terkumpul akan ditambah kembali ke Pusat Wallet Utama anda selepas 12 bulan dari tarikh ia diberikan dalam kes pelanggan anda tidak membuat jualan.
values: On sale of every Product; you will receive Primary Points and Secondary Points on the App. You can use the Primary Points to redeem rewards within the app; whereas, Secondary Points are those that get accumulated in your account to reward your customers when they make a sale. These accumulated Secondary Points will be added back to your Primary Points Wallet after 12 months from the date they were awarded in case your customers have not made a sale.
values-vi: Giảm giá mọi Sản phẩm; bạn sẽ nhận được Điểm Chính và Điểm Phụ trên Ứng dụng. Bạn có thể sử dụng Điểm Chính để đổi phần thưởng trong ứng dụng; trong khi đó, Điểm Phụ là những điểm được tích lũy trong tài khoản của bạn để thưởng cho khách hàng của bạn khi họ bán được hàng. Các Điểm Phụ đã tích lũy này sẽ được cộng lại vào Ví Điểm Chính của bạn sau 12 tháng kể từ ngày được tặng trong trường hợp khách hàng của bạn không bán được hàng.
values-th: On sale of every Product; you will receive Primary Points and Secondary Points on the App. You can use the Primary Points to redeem rewards within the app; whereas, Secondary Points are those that get accumulated in your account to reward your customers when they make a sale. These accumulated Secondary Points will be added back to your Primary Points Wallet after 12 months from the date they were awarded in case your customers have not made a sale.
values-zh: On sale of every Product; you will receive Primary Points and Secondary Points on the App. You can use the Primary Points to redeem rewards within the app; whereas, Secondary Points are those that get accumulated in your account to reward your customers when they make a sale. These accumulated Secondary Points will be added back to your Primary Points Wallet after 12 months from the date they were awarded in case your customers have not made a sale.
